00:03:56.222 --> 00:04:01.708
Now the question is:
is the S6 too dull regarding its appearance?

00:04:01.709 --> 00:04:09.695
Which I can imagine, because it's basically an A6 with
larger wheels, better brakes and a spoiler at the back.

00:04:09.696 --> 00:04:13.414
